{"tid":270093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港天文台不為香港預測天氣 香港政府不為香港人服務","createTime":"2017-06-04T06:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T10:58:41.000Z","uid":118983,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e936ab12a8582e25229bca6e6bae87d4c35e56c6","tid":270093,"uid":118983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"天文台高級科學主任李新偉向東網指，作出有大驟雨及狂風雷暴預測，是基於廣東沿岸地區受一道廣闊低壓槽影響，預測相關地區天氣會不穩定，而相關預測跟廣東省今日整體天氣形勢比較，並沒有錯。 <br />\n<br />\n李新偉表示，驟雨及雷暴天氣今日正正在香港東北面50公里的廣東省出現，並解釋驟雨及雷暴系統隨機成分較高，<span style=\"color: red;\">相關天氣沒有在香港出現，不代表預測不準確。</span>東網發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">汕尾、汕頭及惠州等在香港東北面地區</span>，今日的確有中雨至大雨天氣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4326053c91a3ddf5cfb6780a01d2c19ad4cc9f11","tid":270093,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02a3aa3606fbd0ea515f58774bf0b678361e8b5","tid":270093,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5062fdc9c62d6fbe74389c7b49ee4b4e54c3d3","tid":270093,"uid":41507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce4a9927692495d44d80db7b029e50571a656df","tid":270093,"uid":97212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:09:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天文台高級科學主任李新偉向東網指，作出有大驟雨及狂風雷暴預測，是基於廣東沿岸地區受一道廣闊低壓槽影響，預測相關地區天氣會不穩定，而相關預測跟廣東省今日整體天氣形勢比較，並沒有錯。 <br />\n<br />\n李新偉表示，驟雨及雷暴天氣今日正正在香港東北面50公里的廣東省出現，並解釋驟雨及雷暴系統隨機成分較高，<span style=\"color: red;\">相關天氣沒有在香港出現，不代表預測不準確。</span>東網發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">汕尾、汕頭及惠州等在香港東北面地區</span>，今日的確有中雨至大雨天氣。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同晒全地球比就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bc5493372975eaf1a7ee968cfe280feab1bec1","tid":270093,"uid":118983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:15:03.000Z","msg":"香港天文台預測北極將會落雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05aa4c3cb2b485959e34bc77edcfbc668f5fe713","tid":270093,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:24:13.000Z","msg":"我預測明天地球上分別出現，大雨丶烈日當空丶雷暴丶冰雹丶熱帶氣旋，準確度百分百"},{"pid":"548869466844546ba091837bb7f811526ecc4e26","tid":270093,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1fde11e18150510ae34c64e66a196d8b0cab5f","tid":270093,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"呢個對漁船，旅船，郵船無用咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab8e8f600a87607c6c4b3d5cb34b9deebfc4d07","tid":270093,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1d47390867f0206f4cf1d4758b278a878d07f92","tid":270093,"uid":118983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T10:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}